This release includes the following features:\
- Floating-point and decimal instructions,\
- Large memory support - to 1024 KW,\
- Improved terminal functions, including a command history and editor,\
- Private disk packs,\
- Support for both .mt and .tap format tapes,\
- Automatic bursting of printer output to PDF files,\
- Simple host machine interfaces, such as drag and drop of Mac files into the card reader, and easy copying of CP-V text files to the Mac via the Card Punch.\
